''Thrill of the Feel'' is Crush 40's first album. It is the only album released under their original name, Sons of Angels. The album contains all of the tracks that the band recorded for ''[[NASCAR Arcade]]''.<ref name="crush40"/>  This album was released by [[Victor Entertainment]] and was released for the Japanese market.<ref name="jvc"/>

