''Crush 40'' is the self-titled second album of Crush 40, released in Europe by [[Frontiers Records]].<ref name="c40"/>  The album contains many of the same tracks as ''Thrill of the Feel'', but does not contain any instrumental tracks.<ref name="faq"/>  Added to the track listing are "Live and Learn" and the bonus tracks "It Doesn't Matter" featuring Tony Harnell and "Escape from the City" featuring Ted Poley and Tony Harnell.

